      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific coupon testing; geometric inputs from CMM; boundary conditions from ASTM F1717 protocol.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus sourced from lot-specific tensile testing of Ti-6Al-4V rod stock. UHMWPE block properties from supplier datasheet confirmed by internal testing. All geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of the specific production lot used in bench testing. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo sampling (500 runs)."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
