      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from a single production lot. Each construct characterized for screw dimensions (CMM), rod dimensions (micrometer), and UHMWPE block density. Traceability chain from physical samples to model input parameters is complete and documented."
    },
    {
