      "rationale": "Direct mapping established between each model input parameter and the corresponding measured physical property of the test specimens. Material property equivalency confirmed within ±3% for all parameters. Geometric equivalency confirmed within CMM measurement uncertainty (±0.01 mm). Formal equivalency table documented in the simulation report."
    },
